    "title": "Hekima ya Solomoni",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "hekima ya solomoni",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Wakati Mungu alipompa Mfalme Solomoni nafasi ya kuomba chochote, Solomoni alichagua hekima. Alitaka kuwaongoza watu wa Mungu vizuri na kutofautisha mema na mabaya (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:9\">1 Wafalme 3:9</a>). Kwa sababu ya chaguo hili lisilo la ubinafsi, Mungu alimpa hekima aliyotaka na malipo ya kuitumia ipasavyo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:12\">3:12, 1</a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:13-1Kgs3:14\">3–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:14-2Chr1:17\">2 Mambo ya Nyakati 1:14–17</a>).</p><p>Matendo ya Solomoni yalionyesha hekima yake kwa haraka. Alitatua mzozo kuhusu mtoto kwa hekima kiasi kwamba iliwashangaza watu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:16-1Kgs3:28\">1 Wafalme 3:16–28</a>). Baadaye, Malkia wa Sheba alitembelea ili kumjaribu kwa maswali magumu. Aligundua kuwa hekima yake ilikuwa kubwa kuliko alivyokuwa amesikia (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:1-1Kgs10:9\">10:1–9</a>).</p><p>Mambo mengi yalionyesha hekima ya Solomoni, ikiwa ni pamoja na:</p><ul><li><p>jinsi alivyopanga na kusimamia serikali yake pamoja na maafisa wake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:1-1Kgs4:28\">4:1–28</a>);</p></li><li><p>jinsi alivyoshughulikia uhusiano na mataifa mengine na wafalme (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:1-1Kgs5:9\">5:1–9</a>);</p></li><li><p>miundo aliyoijenga, hasa hekalu na jumba lake la kifalme (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:10-1Kgs7:51\">5:10–7:51</a>); na</p></li><li><p>shughuli zake na biashara na mataifa mengine (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:26-1Kgs9:28\">9:26–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:14-1Kgs10:29\">10:14–29</a>).</p></li></ul><p>Solomoni alipata maarifa mengi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:29-1Kgs4:33\">4:29–33</a>). Aliandika Mithali (sehemu kubwa ya kitabu cha Mithali) pamoja na nyimbo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:1-Ps72:20\">Zaburi 72</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps127:1-Ps127:5\">127</a>). Pia aliandika mashairi ya mapenzi (tazama Wimbo Ulio Bora) na kazi za kifalsafa (tazama Mhubiri). Alitumia hekima yake kujenga hekalu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:12\">2 Mambo ya Nyakati 2:12</a>). Hii ilikuwa kama Besaleli ambaye alipewa hekima ya kujenga hema (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:1-Exod31:3\">Kutoka 31:1–3</a>).</p><p>Yesu alisisitiza hekima kuu ya Solomoni na kuwaambia wasikilizaji wake kwamba, &quot;Mmoja aliye mkuu kuliko Solomoni yupo hapa&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:42\">Mathayo 12:42</a>). Yesu ndiye hekima ya kweli ya Mungu, ambapo mtu anaweza kupata hekima ya juu kabisa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:24\">1 Wakorintho 1:24</a>). Maisha yenye hekima yamejikita katika Yesu na katika Maandiko (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:18-1Cor1:25\">1 Wakorintho 1:18–25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:16\">Wakolosai 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:18\">2 Petro 3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:14-2Tim3:17\">2 Timotheo 3:14–17</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:1-Exod31:6\">Kutoka 31:1–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:5-1Kgs3:14\">1 Wafalme 3:5–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:16-1Kgs3:28\">3:16–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:29-1Kgs4:34\">4:29–34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:2-1Kgs5:7\">5:2–7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:1-1Kgs10:13\">10:1–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:7-2Chr1:12\">2 Mambo ya Nyakati 1:7–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:1-Ps72:20\">Zaburi 72:1–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps111:10\">111:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps127:1-Ps127:5\">127:1–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:9-Eccl12:14\">Mhubiri 12:9–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:1-Isa11:5\">Isaya 11:1–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:23-Jer9:24\">Yeremia 9:23–24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:42\">Mathayo 12:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:5\">Yakobo 1:5</a></p>",
